# Vendored embedding model weights (crates/calm-core/build.rs, 2026-07-12) —
# fetched from HuggingFace Hub (minishlab/potion-code-16M) and checksum-
# verified at build time instead of being git-tracked via LFS (that used to
# exhaust the GitHub account's LFS bandwidth budget — see
# docs/superskills/specs/2026-07-12-edge-release-binary-distribution.md).
# config.json/tokenizer.json in the same directory are small enough to stay
# normal tracked git blobs — only the ~64MB weights file needed this.
crates/calm-core/assets/potion-code-16m/model.safetensors

# Gradle build/cache output — left behind by scip-java's real Gradle
# invocation when the D.2 kotlin_overlay_upgrades_ambiguous_smart_cast_calls_*
# ignored test runs against multi_lang_workspace/kotlin. `scip-java index`'s
# own `--cleanup` only removes its own semanticdb/targetroot temp state, not
# Gradle's own directories.
crates/calm-core/tests/fixtures/multi_lang_workspace/kotlin/.gradle/
crates/calm-core/tests/fixtures/multi_lang_workspace/kotlin/build/
crates/calm-core/tests/fixtures/multi_lang_workspace/kotlin/index.scip

# Same shape, Maven side: `mvn compile`'s own `target/` plus `scip-java
# index`'s output, left behind when java_overlay_upgrades_a_real_edge_*
# runs against multi_lang_workspace/java (verified live 2026-07-15 building
# Containerfile.scip-toolbox).
crates/calm-core/tests/fixtures/multi_lang_workspace/java/target/
crates/calm-core/tests/fixtures/multi_lang_workspace/java/index.scip

